https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/La-Tr%E1%BA%A1ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%89nh-th%E1%BA%BF-thi/poem--RFLWCHEgU__G8yCOV8mew">Tỉnh thế thi - 醒世詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/La-Tr%E1%BA%A1ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-MpvRP0nh_-vWfD6k7n8bbQ">La Trạng Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/Tu-T%C3%A2y-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%9Di/poem-GRNH9SS7MhDNhNNF3-MOJQ">Tu Tây phương thập nhị thời - 修西方十二時</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/author-D3nlI_QzeVjknjQ7vGsW3w">Thiện Đạo đại sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam-th%E1%BA%BF-ch%C3%AD-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-pwYVzZ3mpuX7PHg6BRMRqA">Việt Nam thế chí tự - 越南世志序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
